These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
House: palace, art-deco, craftsman, farmhouse
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, bluemaster, davidoff, bolivar
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, parkour, cricket, climbing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, documentary, adventure, time-travel
 1. the swisher-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
 2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
 3. the palace house is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is climbing is the bluemaster-smoker##1
 5. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching adventure movies##5
 6. the swisher-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person watching documentary movies##5
 7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far left##1
 8. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the left of the bluemaster-smoker##5
 9. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the davidoff-smoker##3
10. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere between the person watching mystery movies and the palace house##7
11. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
12. the bolivar-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person watching time-travel movies##5
13. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| House   | farmhouse    | art-deco | craftsman    | palace   |
| Cigar   | swisher | davidoff | bluemaster | bolivar |
| Sport           | parkour       | cricket   | climbing  | baseball     |
| Movie-Genre     | mystery      | adventure   | time-travel    | documentary    |

