 7. the dancer is somewhere between the fan rock and the old-henry-smoker##7
 8. the journalist is in an odd position##4
 9. the journalist is somewhere to the left of the fan rock##5
10. the ranch-style house is somewhere to the right of the fan classical##5
11. the prince-smoker is the fan indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
