The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, rugby, skiing, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to boston##5
 2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere between the person driving the jet-ski and the person traveling to boston##7
 3. the person driving the subway is the person drinking mirinda##1
 4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person traveling to marseilles##3
 6. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to berlin##5
 7. the person driving the ship is not the person traveling to venice##6
 8. the person traveling to boston is not the person driving the skateboard##6
 9. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
10. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
11. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
12. the person drinking milk is the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3     |        4        |
| Transport           | skateboard | jet-ski | subway | ship |
| City   | berlin        | marseilles    | venice    | boston    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk        | iced-tea   | mirinda   | milk         |
| Sport           | rugby          | cricket       | weightlifting   | skiing           |

