 4. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who likes black##1
 5. the person who likes turquise is somewhere to the left of the person who growssunflower##5
 6. the fan punk is on the left or right of the person who growsbellflower##3
 7. the person who likes turquise is somewhere between the fan salsa and the fan punk##7
 8. the person who likes grey is not the fan salsa##6
 9. the fan house is on the left or right of the fan punk##3
10. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
11. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
12. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the fan punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Color         | ebony      | turquise   | grey   | black       |
| Beverage   | juice | mirinda    | cola | sprite       |
| Flower   | dahlia  | bellflower | sunflower   | lily     |
| Music-Genre         | salsa   | gospel    | punk   | house |

