.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, indonesian, russian, thai
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, azalea, amaryllis, bellflower
There 4 different types of food: avocado, orange, cranberry, kale
City: paris, colone, rome, san-francisco
 1. the person traveling to san-francisco is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to paris##5
 2. the person who growsamaryllis is the russian##1
 3. the person traveling to colone is the person eating kale##1
 4. the person eating cranberry is between the thai and the indonesian##2
 5. the person who growsiris is somewhere to the right of the indonesian##5
 6. the person eating avocado is somewhere between the person who growsamaryllis and the argentine##7
 7. the thai is somewhere to the left of the person who growsazalea##5
 8. the person eating avocado is the person traveling to paris##1
 9. the person who growsazalea is somewhere to the left of the person who growsiris##5
10. the person eating orange is on the far right##1
11. the person traveling to rome is in an even position##4
12. the person who growsiris is somewhere to the right of the indonesian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | thai      | russian     | indonesian   | argentine    |
| Flower     | bellflower | amaryllis   | azalea | iris |
| Food     | kale        | cranberry     | avocado  | orange      |
| City   | colone       | san-francisco | paris   | rome    |

 